{"type": "article", "id": 20923, "title": "韩国这家幼儿园，想让小朋友认识什么构成了“城市”", "description": "每一个房间都只有一种颜色，但光线和转折的墙面让每个房间都非常独特。", "date": "2016-01-19T13:29:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17008, "name": "公共建筑"}, {"id": 4187, "name": "幼儿园"}, {"id": 620, "name": "韩国"}, {"id": 22343, "name": "Janghwan Cheon + Studio"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 281, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021347237IeMZhfpP4Q3jyFb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>越来越多的幼儿园融入了设计者对于早期教育的想法。有的放任玩耍，寓教于乐，也有通过建筑设计来影响儿童的世界观。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这家幼儿园在韩国首尔，外观上最明显的标志是不规则的屋顶，虽然还是用的青瓦，它的起伏和转折并不连贯，倒像是将不同幢房子拼在一起了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134711MCGJadBTLv241ZqI.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"487\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134712RjWc4xTS0mBG9PgC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134712mZGR4y5JiA189C0U.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"715\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134713gImPRrbvS0ZTV7sK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"702\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>如果有机会俯瞰屋顶则会发现，每一块小的坡面屋顶都开了一个小的天窗，它对应着二楼不同的独立房间。设计者的初衷是建立“house within a house”，他们认为幼儿园的建筑能带给儿童最初对城市的感知，幼儿园里的中庭、走廊和房间分别代表城市里的广场、街道和建筑。从这个角度来看，每一个房间都是公寓的延伸，也应该是家庭舒适感的延伸。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134714QRDJlgM91PkaixbH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1296\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>幼儿园有一个很大的中庭，充当城市里广场的职能，连接了一楼和二楼以及各个房间。它可以作为儿童室内活动的场地和办活动的地方，儿童在这里的活动也是在监督之下的，很有安全感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134714KS0huTq6LE4Pno5g.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134715MyfIel0K8X6sxJNi.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"918\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134715yGcV1lvseFIT8maN.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"756\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134716eQ2pBthNM6KudDAf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"709\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347164VmTXs8US1Op7jYK.jpg\" width=\"661\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5128593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>二楼室内里也能感受到不规则的屋顶，每个房间刷成了不同的颜色，有一种活泼和纯净。这种故意保留下来的错位是设计者想要做出的折纸感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>光线从最上面的天窗照射进来，周围零星点缀了方形的小灯，有点教堂的感觉。</span>室内室外两种灯光配合着建筑墙面的转折，让房间的颜色有了深浅变化，很丰富。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>此外，房间里打开了高高低低的窗户，低矮的窗户是为儿童设计的，以便让他们能看到外面的自然。</span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134717fFNThMJ507Bj4zaD.jpg\" width=\"1062\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94161959\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213471787BQYqjMKS3AUlZG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134718QUuOIkLZV0BHbjec.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"714\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347186QSDkXZj5hRMCYBU.jpg\" width=\"1044\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95785441\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347191EhxvYjG0LQPu26e.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134720hXEJ3dac8sOgjkKD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134720XjyNZI8aRdAb4tHr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这家幼儿园位于德寿宫附近，将招收 0 到 5 岁的儿童。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134721pa2EdgnWNtzOmwT5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"823\" title=\"进门处\" alt=\"进门处\" data-ratio=\"0.76203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>进门处</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347217aB4gPfUS2coW1zM.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"洗手池\" alt=\"洗手池\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洗手池</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134722niaR45f96p8P1NeE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"737\" title=\"室外\" alt=\"室外\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室外</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347228kL3Kjt0lCpY9iGX.jpg\" width=\"909\" height=\"1000\" title=\"一楼平面图\" alt=\"一楼平面图\" data-ratio=\"1.10011001\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>一楼平面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021347233thJj09P8F6nLqIC.jpg\" width=\"872\" height=\"1000\" title=\"二楼平面图\" alt=\"二楼平面图\" data-ratio=\"1.14678899\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>二楼平面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/780339/hangdong-kindergarten-janghwan-cheon-plus-studio-i\" target=\"_blank\">archdaily</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}